= Boolean Operators & Short-Circuit

```racket
(and p q r) ; false if any argument is false (stops early)
(or  p q r) ; true  if any argument is true  (stops early)
(not p)     ; flips truth
```

*Quick check*
```racket
(and (> 3 1) (= 2 2) (< 5 4)) ; #false, last term is false
```

