// =====================================================
// Identifier Rules (Legal Names)
// =====================================================
= Identifier Rules (Legal Names)

- Letters, digits, and `- _ . ? =` allowed; must contain *≥1 non-digit*.  
- No spaces, quotes, or brackets.

*Good:* `cool?`, `is-even?`, `sum3`  
*Bad:* `3to1` (all digits), `my var` (space), `"name"` (quotes)

